1. Project Overview
Title: ColorMe to Shopify Migration App

Description:
A Shopify-embedded application that enables merchants to migrate customer, product, and order data from ColorMe by GMO to Shopify. The app is designed with two tiers:

- Free Tier: Imports the first 10 customers and 10 products for testing.
- Paid Tier: Provides unlimited migration with full data selection control.

